<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>오류 발생</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 50px;
        }
        .error-box {
            border: 1px solid #ff6b6b;
            background-color: #ffecec;
            padding: 20px;
            display: inline-block;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .home-button {
            margin-top: 20px;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }
        .home-button:hover {
            background-color: #0056b3;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="error-box">
    <h2>❌ 오류가 발생했어요.</h2>
    <p>{{errorMessage}}</p>
    <button class="home-button" onclick="window.location.href='/'">🏠 홈으로 돌아가기</button>
</div>
</body>
</html>
